            "controls": [
                { "type": "text", "param": "sessionDate", "label": "Session Date", "stacked": true, "cellClassName": "sm-col-12 lg-col-6" },
                { "type": "text", "param": "playersPresent", "label": "Players Present", "stacked": true, "cellClassName": "sm-col-12 lg-col-6" },
                { "type": "textarea", "param": "overview", "label": "OotA — Session 1", "rows": 8, "value": "Property of Velkynvelve → Last Chance. Five days in the drow slave pen at Velkynvelve: learn the routine, win allies, find the openings, and break out before the transfer to Menzoberranzan.\n\nThe five-day arc: Day 1 establishes the routine and the initial prisoners. Day 2 stages the Jorlan/Shoor rivalry. Day 3 lands new prisoners and reveals the lift. Day 4 has Asha probe for divisions while Jorlan quietly manufactures an opening. Day 5 forces the break before the transfer." },
                { "type": "textarea", "param": "sessionGoal", "label": "Session Goal", "rows": 3, "value": "By the end of Day 5 the party should hold a workable escape plan and commit to it. Cooperation with at least some fellow prisoners is the through-line of the whole session." },
                { "type": "textarea", "param": "sessionNotes", "label": "Session Notes", "rows": 6 }
            ]
        },
        {
